OL,3,CMan sentenced after failing to stop
OL,4,Cduring pursuit
OL,6,FA motorcyclist who led officers on a
OL,7,Fchase around Cheshire has been banned
OL,8,Ffrom driving.
OL,10,FWarrington Magistrates Court heard how
OL,11,FCheshire Police attempted to stop
OL,12,FPhilip Hunter at around 4.30pm on
OL,13,FWednesday 17 July, near to junction 12
OL,14,Fof the M56 near Hapsford.
OL,16,FThe 25-year-old and another
OL,17,Fmotorcyclist failed to stop and drove
OL,18,Foff onto the A56 travelling towards
OL,19,FFrodsham.
