OL,3,CMan sentenced after failing to stop
OL,4,Cduring pursuit
OL,6,FOfficers lost sight of one of the
OL,7,Fbikes, but they continued to follow
OL,8,Fthe second bike ridden by Hunter as he
OL,9,Fled police on a pursuit through the
OL,10,FWeaverham in Northwich.
OL,12,FAs the Police Motorcycle officers were
OL,13,Ftravelling towards Weaverham, they
OL,14,Fwere joined by several other officers
OL,15,Fand a Police helicopter.
OL,17,FUpon entering the village, Hunter
OL,18,Fabandoned his bike and attempted to
OL,19,Fmake off on foot but was quickly
OL,20,Flocated by the police helicopter and
OL,21,Farrested.
