OL,3,CMan sentenced after failing to stop
OL,4,Cduring pursuit
OL,6,FHe appeared at Warrington Magistrates
OL,7,Fon Thursday 12 September where he was
OL,8,Fsentenced to 26 weeks in prison
OL,9,Fsuspended for two years.
OL,11,FThe 25-year-old, of Beswick Road,
OL,12,FNorthwich, had previously pleaded
OL,13,Fguilty to dangerous driving.
OL,15,FHe was also banned from driving for 12
OL,16,Fmonths and ordered to undertake an
OL,17,Fextended retest.
OL,19,FFollowing the sentencing Chief
OL,20,FInspector John Forshaw, of the Roads
OL,21,Fand Crime Unit, said:
