OL,3,CMan sentenced after failing to stop
OL,4,Cduring pursuit
OL,6,F"Hunter is clearly a dangerous
OL,7,Findividual, who put the lives of
OL,8,Fofficers and innocent members of the
OL,9,Fpublic at risk for no apparent reason
OL,10,Fwhatsoever .
OL,12,F"His reckless behaviour led officers
OL,13,Fon a pursuit across rural Cheshire,
OL,14,Fthroughout which he showed no regard
OL,15,Ffor those around them.
OL,17,F"However, despite his repeated
OL,18,Fattempts to evade officers, there
OL,19,Freally was nowhere to hide and he has
OL,20,Fnow been held accountable for his
OL,21,Factions.
